statement:
Create a simple API to store and retrieve user profiles. Users can be added, retrieved by ID, and listed. Implement a basic error handling mechanism to handle missing user IDs and invalid user data.

Endpoints:

* POST /api/users - Create a new user profile
* GET /api/users/:id - Retrieve a user profile by ID
* GET /api/users - List all user profiles

Constraints:

* Use only the in-memory array provided in the starter code
* User IDs are integers
* User data should have a 'name' and 'email' property
* Error responses should have a 'code' and 'message' property

Starter Code:

The starter code is a basic Express server setup with a users array in memory.

